---
title: Double Hearty Venison & Beef Cottage Pie with Cheesy Potato Mash Topping
description: This classic comfort dish is the perfect way to warm up this winter. Imagine a hearty hug on a plate, with a rich, meaty filling
topped with a fluffy blanket of cheesy mashed potatoes. Happiness is just a bite away!
